title: Day 4: 11:49 PM
body:
// I uploaded quite a bit today, // now sorting through work from 2001!  Because I get bored doing the same thing over and over again, I like to switch between uploading posts, editing photos, and organizing my files.


And oh goodness, // there is so much amazing artwork on social media! // A beautiful array of different styles and subjects, too much to get through them all.


//  Got bad heartburn, but still managed to keep the uploads coming! 👌//


Random iTunes Shuffle Day4: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pkGjIvggIY8
